<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.2/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-0evHe/X+R7YkIZDRvuzKMRqM+OrBnVFBL6DOitfPri4tjfHxaWutUpFmBp4vmVor" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/css/style.css">

    <title>Acep Awaludin</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-light h-10vh">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="./">
                    <img src="./../assets/img/logo.png" alt="Logo Dumbways" width="30" height="24">
                </a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link active hover-orange" aria-current="page" href="./">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link hover-orange" href="./#myProject">My Project</a>
                        </li>
                        {{#if isLogin}}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link hover-orange" href="./add-project">Add Project</a>
                        </li>
                        {{/if}}
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link btn btn-orange text-light py-1" href="./contact">Contact Me</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="card my-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 80%;">
            <div class="row g-0 align-items-center justify-content-between">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center text-md-start">Hai, Selamat Datang di Website Saya! :D</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-justify">Saya adalah seorang Fullstack Web Developer.
                            Pertamakali saya
                            menyukai
                            bidang 'perkodingan' adalah ketika saya duduk di bangku SMA. Karena pada saat itu, ternyata
                            di Yayasan tempat saya belajar juga terdapat sekolah SMK dengan jurusan Rekayasa Perangkat
                            Lunak (RPL). Sejak saat itu lah saya mulai mempelajari HTML dan CSS secara otodidak
                            menggunakan modul yang dipinjamkan oleh teman saya.</p>
                        <p class="card-text text-justify">Saat ini, saya sedang memperdalam pengetahuan saya mengenai
                            pemrograman
                            komputer dengan mengikuti Bootcamp Dumbways. Pada Bootcamp ini, saya masih berada di stage
                            pertama. Kendati demikian, saya yakin saya bisa melalui semua tantangan ke depannya hingga
                            saya dapat menuntaskan pembelajaran saya di sini.</p>
                        <p class="card-text text-justify">Terdapat beberapa teknologi yang telah saya kuasai saat ini.
                            Yaitu: HTML,
                            CSS, JavaScript, TailwindCSS, dan SASS. Jika anda tertarik untuk merekrut saya agar
                            bergabung bersama tim anda, silakan hubungi saya melalui tombol di bawah. Anda juga dapat
                            menghubungi saya melalui sosial media saya.</p>
                        <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-orange rounded-pill me-4 text-white">Contact</a>
                        <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-muted rounded-pill hover-orange">
                            Download CV
                            <i class='bx bx-download'></i>
                        </a>
                        <div class="mt-4 social-media">
                            <a class="text-decoration-none" target="_blank" href="./contact">
                                <img src="./../assets/img/email.svg" alt="Email">
                            </a>
                            <a class="text-decoration-none" target="_blank" href="https://wa.me/6281383647020">
                                <img src="./../assets/img/whatsapp.svg" alt="WhatsApp">
                            </a>
                            <a class="text-decoration-none" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/acep179">
                                <img src="./../assets/img/github.svg" alt="GitHub">
                            </a>
                            <a class="text-decoration-none" target="_blank" href="https://linkedin.com/in/acep179/">
                                <img src="./../assets/img/linkedin.svg" alt="LinkedIn">
                            </a>
                            <a class="text-decoration-none" target="_blank" href="https://instagram.com/">
                                <img src="./../assets/img/instagram.svg" alt="Instagram">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card ms-md-auto me-md-3 mx-auto my-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
                        <img src="./../assets/img/acep.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Acep Awaludin">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title text-center">Acep Awaludin</h5>
                            <p class="card-text text-center">Fullstack Developer</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="myProject" class="container mb-5 d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center">
            <h2 class="w-100 text-center mb-4">My Project</h2>
            {{#each projects}}
            <div class="card mx-3 mb-4" style="width: 18rem;">
                <img src="{{this.image}}" class="card-img-top" alt="gudangku">
                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <a class="text-black hover-orange text-decoration-none" href="./../project-detail/{{@index}}"
                            target="_blank">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{this.name}}</h5>
                        </a>
                        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
                            Durasi:
                            {{#if this.yearDuration}}
                            {{this.yearDuration}} tahun
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.monthDuration}}
                            {{this.monthDuration}} bulan
                            {{/if}}
                        </h6>
                        <p class="card-text">{{this.descriptionShort}}<a class="hover-orange text-decoration-none"
                                href="./../project-detail/{{@index}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> ...</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between">
                        <div class="w-100 fs-1">
                            {{#each this.technologies}}
                            {{{this}}}
                            {{/each}}
                        </div>
                        {{#if isLogin}}
                        <a href="/edit-project/{{@index}}" class="btn btn-dark py-0 project-btn">Edit</a>
                        <a href="/delete-project/{{@index}}" class="btn btn-dark py-0 project-btn">Delete</a>
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </main>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-pprn3073KE6tl6bjs2QrFaJGz5/SUsLqktiwsUTF55Jfv3qYSDhgCecCxMW52nD2" crossorigin="anonymous">
        </script>
</body>

</html>